{
  "texts": [
    "PRINCESS implicitly calls Minimap2 (ref.",
    "64) (version 2.17) with the following parameters '-ax map-ont -Y --MD'.",
    "Later, we sorted the output using SAMtools 55 (version 1.14).",
    "For all samples, unfiltered SV candidates and genome-wide coverage information are written to a specified output SNF file and then merged with Sniffles2 population-level calling.",
    "General statistics, such as SV sizes and composition (proportion of each SV type), were computed by extracting the SVLEN, SVTYPE and GT information from the VCF file."
  ]
}